cession” of 2008.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aCold War. 0aGreat Britain -- Foreign relations -- 1945-. 0aSecurity, International. 0aUnited States -- Foreign relations -- 1945-1989. 0aUnited States -- Foreign relations -- 1989-. 0aWorld politics -- 1945-1989. 0aWorld politics -- 1989-. 0aWorld politicsy1945-1989. 0aWorld politicsy1989-. 7aHISTORY / United States / 20th Century.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015z978311067250340uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030021021740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300210217423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300210217/original  a978-3-11-067250-3  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2014-2015c2014d2015  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles